original_title: Chan Fai Young x Women's Choir Live Concert 陈辉阳 x 女声合唱人来人往
overview: Chan Fai Young x Women's Choir's People Come People Go Live Concert arrives in a limited Blu-ray and CD boxset! On June 25, 2021, Chan Fai Young x Women's Choir took the stage of the Hong Kong Coliseum for the first time to portray a musical story centering around the theme of "Don't forget us, Don't forget Hong Kong." They performed a total of 34 songs, including "People Come and Go," "Beauty For Life," "The King of Karaoke," "Love in Troubled Times," "For Elise," "The Maidens Prayer" and more. Besides concert performances, the Blu-ray release features behind-the-scenes and audio commentary by Chan Fai Young.
title: Chan Fai Young x Women's Choir Live Concert 陈辉阳 x 女声合唱人来人往
